C.C., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3526 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 09, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Because C.C. has failed to serve an initial brief as provided by this court's order of December 19, 2018, this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

LaROSE, C.J., and SALARIO and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
